snippet.title: Astral Guidance Operating System
snippet.description:
If you want to find out what happened to Outpost SIGMA-ALPHA-TWENTY-THREE-OMEGA and the survivors of the Astra Protocol, you're going to need some serious hardware.

Introducing the Astral Guidance Operating System, utilising a whole 64K of memory. No captain should leave port without it.

*Please note that Slice Bar waives any liability for any deep space mishap that may occur through use of this software including, but not limited to, self destruction, orbiting a black hole, or getting sucked out of an airlock.

Download the original game here: https://slicebar.itch.io/astra-protocol
